istrationFill all the details in the complaint form and hit the \u201cSubmit\u201d button to send your complaint.PMFBY Helpline Number\u2013 For any query, farmers can call on 011-23382012 followed by an extension 2715 / 2709. \u2013 Farmers can call on the Direct Helpline Number on 011-23381092 \u2013 All farmers can also write their Queries at help.agri-insurance@gov.inReferences \u2014 PM Fasal Bima Yojana Guidelines \u2013 PMFBY 2020 Guidelines \u2014 Aadhar Notification Of Insurance Scheme \u2013 Click Here \u2014 PMFBY mandatory entry of all coverage details on portal from Kharif 2017 onwards \u2013 Click Here \u2014 PMFBY / WBCIS Declaration Form \u2013 Download Form \u2014 PMFBY / WBCIS Acknowledgement Receipt \u2013 Acknowledgement Format \u2014 How to create State/Bank/Insurance Company/Admin? \u2013 Click Here  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}